2. Write a program to find the integer square root of a given number.
solve:
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

int main() {
int y,d;
cout<<"enter a num = ";
cin>>y;
d=sqrt(y);
cout<<d<<endl;
return 0;
}
